title: Chris Chan Came Back To YouTube...
description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! This time we take a look at what appears to be the return of one of the oldest Internet personalities on the web, Chris Chan who is the creator of Sonichu. This individual has had a rather infamous last couple years so for this to occur was a tad unexpected. Thanks for watching!
Like, Comment and Subscribe for more videos!
